<div class="body-wrapper">
<div>
  <div class="background pt-3">
    <div class="pages-container">
     <h1>Set up your patch</h1>
    </div>
    <ul class="nav nav-pills mb-3 list-inline tabs-underlined active" id="pills-tab" role="tablist">
      <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
        <button class="nav-link active tab-underlined" id="pills-home-tab" href="#pills-home" data-toggle="pill" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-home" aria-selected="true">You need</button>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
        <button class="nav-link tab-underlined" id="pills-assembly-tab" href="#pills-assembly" data-toggle="pill" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-assembly" aria-selected="false">Assembly</button>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-content" id="pills-tabContent">
    <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="pills-home" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-home-tab">
      <div class="cards-container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="card-setup col-6">
              <div class="card-body">
                 <%= image_tag "cardboardboxes.jpg", class: "card-img-top" %>
                <h5 class="card-text">Cardboard boxes</h5>
                <p class="card-text">10-14</p>
                <p class="card-text">Used</p>
                <h6 class="card-text">How to find</h6>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-setup col-6">
              <div class="card-body">
                <%= image_tag "raisedbedframe.jpg", class: "card-img-top" %>
                <h5 class="card-text">1 raised bed frame</h5>
                <p class="card-text">1.2m x 1.2m</p>
                <p class="card-text">Recycled wood</p>
                <h6 class="card-text">Make your own</h6>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-setup col-6">
              <div class="card-body">
                <%= image_tag "gardenshovel.jpg", class: "card-img-top" %>
                <h5 class="card-text">Garden shovel</h5>
                <p class="card-text">80cm</p>
                <p class="card-text">Recycled materials</p>
                <h6 class="card-text">Expert advise</h6>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-setup col-6">
              <div class="card-body">
                <%= image_tag "organiccompost.jpg", class: "card-img-top" %>
                <h5 class="card-text">Organic compost</h5>
                <p class="card-text">400g</p>
                <p class="card-text">Chipping-based</p>
                <h6 class="card-text">Make your own</h6>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-setup col-6">
              <div class="card-body">
                <%= image_tag "organicsoil.jpg", class: "card-img-top" %>
                <h5 class="card-text">Organic soil</h5>
                <p class="card-text">400g</p>
                <p class="card-text">Nutrient-riched</p>
                <h6 class="card-text">Make your own</h6>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-assembly" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-assembly-tab">
      <div class="card-text-step">
        <ul class="list-ellipse-class">
          <li class="list-bullets-1">
            <h5>Step One</h5>
            <p>Start by laying cardboard over the area the new bed will occupy. This will help to clear all the grass and weeds beneath.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-step">
        <ul class="list-ellipse-class">
          <li class="list-bullets-2">
            <h5>Step Two</h5>
            <p>After the grass has rotted down, remove the cardboard and lay out your raised bed frame where you would like your patch to be.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-step">
        <ul class="list-ellipse-class">
          <li class="list-bullets-3">
            <h5>Step Three</h5>
            <p>Assemble the frame or <strong>create your own with our simple guide.</strong></p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <%= image_tag "assempagepic.jpg", class: "assembly-pic" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-step">
        <ul class="list-ellipse-class">
          <li class="list-bullets-4">
            <h5>Step Four</h5>
            <p>With the walls of the raised bed fixed together, it's time to fill it. Add organic garden compost and soil to the bed. This will introduce lots of beneficial microorganisms to the soil, which will further enhance plant growth.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= render 'shared/menu' %>
</div>
</div>
